        <h3>Hollywood diner, Frymaster MJ150 (year 8)</h3>
        <p>Recovery stretched to 5 minutes during lunch rush. Manometer test at gas valve outlet: pressure at 3.2 inches WC (spec 4.5-5.0). Diagnosed regulator drift on the gas valve. Replaced regulator, retested at 4.7 inches WC, recovery back to 110 seconds. Total: $120 plus $580 part plus 75 minutes labor = $760.</p>
      </div>
